{"tid":2054431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉: 悼念六四死者有咩問題？","createTime":"2020-06-07T07:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T07:27:12.000Z","uid":358604,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"51f449f744950254a977518d7b008ddea7655634","tid":2054431,"uid":358604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:04:30.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀指，法例只會針對極少數、犯下指定4項行為的人。她舉例指剛過去的六四悼念活動，縱使警方未有批准，但參與人士和平散去，沒有堵路，警方亦盡量不介入，<span style=\"color: red;\">她指：「悼念死者啫，有咩問題？」</span><br />\n<br />\n葉劉表示，她擔任保安局局長年代於香港生效的《聯合國(反恐怖主義措施)條例》，只針對聯合國安理會所列明的恐怖組織，無法取締新型的網上組織，因此港區國安法有其需要。她又相信，港區國安法不會有追溯期，因為根據國際公約條文，刑事罪行都不會有追溯期；而且據屬地原則，會在犯案地審理。<br />\n<br />\n至於立法後叫「港獨」口號會否觸犯法例，葉劉淑儀指，普通法定罪要求很高，控方要證明被告的犯罪意圖及毫無合理疑點等。至於外籍法官的角色，她認為是否適合審案不是從國籍去看，而是從法律知識、經驗去看，反指有部分本地法官，與政黨關係密切，參加聯署、發表政論等。<br />\n<strong>掃把頭反了</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f184760d16a62465a5c2f0f02c0b17c6268b7a59","tid":2054431,"uid":147916,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:05:07.000Z","msg":"反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aebe92707b317f945fbb0d9a7bd8f2bed0cc69a","tid":2054431,"uid":3283,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:05:23.000Z","msg":"嘩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58955d1a9ded1b3975791b0daf9dc82d25926e57","tid":2054431,"uid":36075,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:06:23.000Z","msg":"多謝，我終於知道64 有死到人了...."},{"pid":"ae30117aac3596d9386aa95e88160b240f102a34","tid":2054431,"uid":358604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:06:56.000Z","msg":"掃把頭好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6ae6b9e0a2d817429be674c45a53f139df34a5","tid":2054431,"uid":38390,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:06:59.000Z","msg":"佢一定會話死嘅係人民子弟兵"},{"pid":"de11bac5fc5a6f2b6854d56736ca86d799a1e72b","tid":2054431,"uid":358604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:07:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0298af124f8840eb6ef406bddca54750947a7c0b","tid":2054431,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:08:43.000Z","msg":"洩密國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b17f4768c328f2e3221adb702c2af4bac1e1d7c","tid":2054431,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:09:40.000Z","msg":"你唔準叫「結束x x x x」同「打倒x x x」呀嘛"},{"pid":"0e778adee0500f811742a5537119ae41e9270f72","tid":2054431,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">64邊有死人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n孽瘤黃屍曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div>"},{"pid":"fc0941701b2b0207c4eba308f5fcedf868c97446","tid":2054431,"uid":229369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:21:16.000Z","msg":"悼念八三一死者有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a1548c99a0e669e4278c6c8c76b88e4c0b95dbf","tid":2054431,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:21:23.000Z","msg":"請葉同志解釋甚麼是64"},{"pid":"1faa3efe2268d87dcdfde363d4cdd194ef95dc20","tid":2054431,"uid":305083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":